Signing up for a free tier account with AWS

1: Go to aws web site and create a free account
https://aws.amazon.com/console/and

2. Fill out all the required details and click on “Continue”.

3. Select the account type (personal), fill other detail and click on “Create account and continue”
 
4. Next fill out payment information - enter your credit/debit card info
and click on 'Secure Submit'

5. Check your email and confirm it. There will be couple of cents charge on your account.

Once you verified, you should be able to access to your account.
